      "caption": "<h3>Paysages nocturnes #4</h3>\r\n<p>Comme d'habitude, arm&eacute; de mon <strong>Pentax K-01</strong>, de mon grand angle <a title=\"Tamron SP AF 10-24mm f / 3.5-4.5\" href=\"http://www.bhphotovideo.com/c/product/583991-REG/Tamron_B001C_700_SP_AF_10_24mm_f.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tamron 10-24 mm</a> et d'un tr&eacute;pier de poche, je photographie en pose lente un quartier d'une grande ville.</p>\r\n<p>Ici je me suis simplement pos&eacute; sur <a title=\"Google Map, Pont Bonaparte, Lyon, France\" href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Pont+Bonaparte,+Lyon,+France&amp;hl=en&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;ll=45.76069,4.828727&amp;spn=0.006437,0.016136&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=58.946508,132.1875&amp;oq=pont+bona&amp;hnear=Pont+Bonaparte,+69005+Lyon,+Rh%C3%B4ne,+Rh%C3%B4ne-Alpes,+France&amp;t=m&amp;z=17&amp;iwloc=A\" target=\"_blank\">le pont Bonaparte</a>, dans le <strong>vieux Lyon</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy&hellip;</p>",
