      "caption": "<p><strong>Malek Chebel</strong>, <a title=\"Robert Laffont, L'&eacute;rotisme arabe\" href=\"http://www.bouquins.tm.fr/site/l_erotisme_arabe_&amp;100&amp;9782221139752.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em>L'&eacute;rotisme arabe</em> - Robert Laffont</a>.</p>",
